<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>539</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Wanene mai ceto? Ba wani mai ceto
 Sai Yesu haifaffe. Kana yin mamaki?
 To, bari in bishe ka,
 Allah ne ya aiko da Jibra'ilu
 Ya ce da Maryamu, ta wurin Ruhu
 Ke za ki haifi ɗa, za a ce da shi Yesu.
 Shi ne mai ceto na duniya duka,
 Mu zo mu karƃa fa, mu za mu karƃa fa.
 Ku yi ta murna don ceto ya zo.
 Kalma Ya iso, mu karƃe shi.</lyrics>
<title>Wanene Mai Ceto? LW539</title>
</song>